name: Collar
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
$COLLAR is the real launchpad for shibarium and supports all tokens of shibs ecosystem! check us out we are building a bullish launchpad, token creator, locker and more.

COLLAR was birthed to create an all-in-one launchpad for users of the Shibarium chain. In order to support Shibariums ecosystem. $SHIB, $BONE, $LEASH, $CLAW and $COLLAR holders will be able to use the launchpad without any additional fees.
